0.label: Geocode_left
0.text:
SELECT ?lfromhn ?ltohn ?wkt 
((<HOUSE_NO>-?lfromhn)*((?x1-?x0)/(?ltohn-?lfromhn))+?x1 AS ?x) 
((<HOUSE_NO>-?lfromhn)*((?y1-?y0)/(?ltohn-?lfromhn))+?y1 AS ?y) 
WHERE { 
	?f census:lfromhn ?lfromhn. 
	?f census:ltohn ?ltohn. 
	?f census:parityl <PARITY> . 
	?f census:fullname <STREET_NAME> . 
	?f census:zipl "<ZIP>"^^xsd:integer. 
	?f census:hasGeometry ?geo. 
	?f census:minx ?x0. 
	?f census:miny ?y0. 
	?f census:maxx ?x1. 
	?f census:maxy ?y1. 
	?geo census:asWKT ?wkt. 
	FILTER( (?lfromhn <= "<HOUSE_NO>"^^xsd:integer && "<HOUSE_NO>"^^xsd:integer <= ?ltohn) 
		 || (?ltohn <= "<HOUSE_NO>"^^xsd:integer && "<HOUSE_NO>"^^xsd:integer <= ?lfromhn) ). 
}

1.label: Geocode_right
1.text:
SELECT ?rfromhn ?rtohn ?wkt 
((<HOUSE_NO>-?rfromhn)*((?x1-?x0)/(?rtohn-?rfromhn))+?x1 AS ?x) 
((<HOUSE_NO>-?rfromhn)*((?y1-?y0)/(?rtohn-?rfromhn))+?y1 AS ?y) 
WHERE { 
	?f census:rfromhn ?rfromhn. 
	?f census:rtohn ?rtohn. 
	?f census:parityr <PARITY> . 
	?f census:fullname <STREET_NAME> . 
	?f census:zipr "<ZIP>"^^xsd:integer. 
	?f census:hasGeometry ?geo. 
	?f census:minx ?x0. 
	?f census:miny ?y0. 
	?f census:maxx ?x1. 
	?f census:maxy ?y1. 
	?geo census:asWKT ?wkt. 
	FILTER( (?rfromhn <= "<HOUSE_NO>"^^xsd:integer && "<HOUSE_NO>"^^xsd:integer <= ?rtohn) 
		 || (?rtohn <= "<HOUSE_NO>"^^xsd:integer && "<HOUSE_NO>"^^xsd:integer <= ?rfromhn) ). 
}
